00:52:55.050 --> 00:53:00.050
so I went to the Pentagon
and Don Steinberg knows this

00:53:00.050 --> 00:53:03.450
because years earlier I had gone
to the State Department to meet

00:53:03.450 --> 00:53:08.030
with him to say,
"hi, my name is" etc.

00:53:08.030 --> 00:53:10.400
And so I do this
kind of advocacy.

00:53:10.400 --> 00:53:13.630
So I went and I was
meeting with the general

00:53:13.630 --> 00:53:22.100
who was running the invasion of
the US troops going into Iraq.

00:53:22.100 --> 00:53:26.070
And so he was very
generous with his time.

00:53:26.070 --> 00:53:29.540
